snippet.title: Super Mario RPG Starlite Worlds: Gameplay Splash Teaser
snippet.description:
by C-Division, U Division

GET DEMO HERE:
http://udivision.blogspot.com/2010/06/download-page-super-mario-rpg-starlite.html

-This is just an update video of some scenes and battle stuff in our game. Stuff is subject to change as usual.
It turned out longer than I intended but I just decided to not cut out parts of the battles and leave them there.
